{"tid":844722,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人聽過天道/一貫道？","createTime":"2018-10-02T05:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T20:05:27.000Z","uid":214084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"34d6ceaef005753cfdfd8121c2956bebcc5ada12","tid":844722,"uid":214084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"入道要發毒誓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遇到危難有三寶護身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死後屍身柔軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd85a443fb4961a2901f12a579b2921534323f5","tid":844722,"uid":34022,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"天道揼柒你"},{"pid":"5dd92db88d776630a2b31a121c59c9e0026c8b15","tid":844722,"uid":150588,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"一本道就聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f480883226b96aa611cce3910cd70e1f7852d4f7","tid":844722,"uid":214084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"佢哋聚會個地方自稱做佛堂<br />\n會有佛壇嗰類嘢 <br />\n但好神秘會有個簾遮遮掩掩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通信徒會互稱對方道親<br />\n上到去要著返件灰色嘅長衫 叫道袍<br />\n<br />\n佛堂入面高級啲嘅叫點傳師<br />\n同其他教會一樣 會叫啲信眾帶人上去<br />\n上到去就會有幾個點傳師加信徒帶你入房<br />\n之後困你個幾兩個鐘 瘋狂說服你求佢個道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話會有三寶護身 死後屍身保存得好好等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求道除咗上面講要發毒誓之外<br />\n仲好似要叩百幾二百個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04ec5c9fd25fd2e6cfc920f95115bc691c3f02c","tid":844722,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd85a443fb4961a2901f12a579b2921534323f5","tid":844722,"uid":34022,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"天道揼柒你"},"c